# .env.example
#
# This project is a static site with no server-side environment variables.
# There are no environment variables to configure for local development.
#
# The only sensitive value is the Formspree form endpoint embedded in:
#   book.html
#   contact.html
#
# Search for REPLACE_ME in those files and substitute the real Formspree
# endpoint URL before deploying to production.
